{%- comment -%}
  moromisu.css は main-page-moromisu.liquid で読み込んでいます
{%- endcomment -%}
<style>
  .c-howtodrink {
    background: url('{{ 'moromisu-material-bg-body.png' | asset_url }}') repeat center center;
  }
</style>

<section class="c-howtodrink">
  {%- if section.settings.main_image_pc != blank or section.settings.main_image_sp != blank -%}
    <picture class="c-howtodrink__main-image">
      {% if section.settings.main_image_sp != blank %}
        <source srcset="{{ section.settings.main_image_sp | image_url: width: 390 }}" media="(max-width: 599px)">
      {% endif %}
      {% if section.settings.main_image_pc != blank %}
        <source srcset="{{ section.settings.main_image_pc | image_url: width: 1440 }}" media="(min-width: 600px)">
      {% endif %}
      {% if section.settings.main_image_sp != blank %}
        {{ section.settings.main_image_sp | image_url: width: 390 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
      {% elsif section.settings.main_image_pc != blank %}
        {{ section.settings.main_image_pc | image_url: width: 1440 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
      {% endif %}
    </picture>
  {%- endif -%}
  <div class="c-howtodrink__inner">
    <div class="c-howtodrink__top">
      <div class="c-howtodrink__vtitle">
        <div class="c-howtodrink__vtitle-col">おすすめの</div>
        <div class="c-howtodrink__vtitle-col">飲み方</div>
      </div>
      <div class="c-howtodrink__info">
        <div class="c-howtodrink__info-title">1日の目安量は約30ml</div>
        <p class="c-howtodrink__info-desc">
          1回または2回に分け、無理のないペースで続けることをおすすめします。<br>
          もろみ酢はそのままでもおいしいですが、 飲み慣れていない方は少なめから試したり、<br class="only-pc">
          水や炭酸水で薄めると、すっきりと飲みやすくなります。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="c-howtodrink__subtitle">
      <span>基本の</span><span class="c-howtodrink__subtitle--accent">飲み方</span>
    </div>
    <p class="c-howtodrink__subdesc">
      もろみ酢はそのままでもおいしいですが、<br>
      日々の生活に無理なく取り入れられる飲み方がいくつもあります。
    </p>

    <div class="c-howtodrink__cards">
      <div class="c-howtodrink__card">
        <div class="c-howtodrink__card-img">
          {% if section.settings.basic_image_1 != blank %}
            {{ section.settings.basic_image_1 | image_url: width: 900 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="c-howtodrink__card-title">ストレート</h3>
        <p class="c-howtodrink__card-desc">素材のやさしい風味が楽しめる、もろみ酢本来の飲み方。まずはそのまま味わってみてください。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="c-howtodrink__card">
        <div class="c-howtodrink__card-img">
          {% if section.settings.basic_image_2 != blank %}
            {{ section.settings.basic_image_2 | image_url: width: 900 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="c-howtodrink__card-title">お湯割り</h3>
        <p class="c-howtodrink__card-desc">温めることで口あたりがやわらぎ、より飲みやすく。肌寒い日やくつろぎたい時間におすすめです。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="c-howtodrink__card">
        <div class="c-howtodrink__card-img">
          {% if section.settings.basic_image_3 != blank %}
            {{ section.settings.basic_image_3 | image_url: width: 900 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="c-howtodrink__card-title">炭酸割り</h3>
        <p class="c-howtodrink__card-desc">炭酸の爽快感で、すっきりとした飲み心地に。暑い季節には氷を加えてさっぱり楽しめます。</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="c-howtodrink__separator">
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
      <span class="c-howtodrink__dot"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="c-howtodrink__subtitle">
      <span class="c-howtodrink__subtitle--accent">アレンジ</span><span>編</span>
    </div>

    <div class="c-howtodrink__cards" style="margin-top: 40px;">
      <div class="c-howtodrink__card">
        <div class="c-howtodrink__card-img">
          {% if section.settings.arrange_image_1 != blank %}
            {{ section.settings.arrange_image_1 | image_url: width: 900 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="c-howtodrink__card-title">ヨーグルトにかけて</h3>
        <p class="c-howtodrink__card-desc">ヨーグルトにかけるだけで、ほどよい酸味が加わり食べやすくなり、朝食やおやつに手軽に取り入れられます。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="c-howtodrink__card">
        <div class="c-howtodrink__card-img">
          {% if section.settings.arrange_image_2 != blank %}
            {{ section.settings.arrange_image_2 | image_url: width: 900 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="c-howtodrink__card-title">ドレッシングとして</h3>
        <p class="c-howtodrink__card-desc">オイルや醤油と合わせるだけで、さっぱりしたドレッシングに。サラダにかけて手軽に楽しめます。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="c-howtodrink__card">
        <div class="c-howtodrink__card-img">
          {% if section.settings.arrange_image_3 != blank %}
            {{ section.settings.arrange_image_3 | image_url: width: 900 | image_tag: loading: 'lazy' }}
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="c-howtodrink__card-title">酢豚に</h3>
        <p class="c-howtodrink__card-desc">いつもの酢の代わりにもろみ酢を使うことで、酸味がやさしく、コクのある味わいに仕上がります。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

